accidental life ( slučajni život ) is a 1969 yugoslav drama film directed by ante peterlić , starring dragutin klobučar , ivo serdar , ana karić and zvonimir rogoz .   an existential study of ordinary lives led by two alienated urban white collar workers , accidental life was the only feature film of ante peterlić , croatian film theorist and film critic .   the film received mediocre reviews and went largely unnoticed after its release , but has been reevaluated decades later as one of the best croatian films ever made .